{% comment %}MAGMA ENERGY — How It Works (editorial numbered list){% endcomment %}

<style>
  .mhow {
    background: #080808;
    padding: clamp(60px,10vw,120px) clamp(24px,5vw,80px);
  }

  .mhow__inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .mhow__head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .mhow__head-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px,6vw,80px);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .mhow__head-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }

  .mhow__step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 36px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    transition: background 0.25s ease;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .mhow__step:hover .mhow__num { color: #00C4B4; }
  .mhow__step:hover .mhow__arrow { opacity: 1; color: #00C4B4; }

  .mhow__num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(64px, 10vw, 130px);
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    transition: color 0.25s ease;
    min-width: 120px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .mhow__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .mhow__step-title {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 64px);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .mhow__step-body {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .mhow__arrow {
    font-size: 28px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    transition: opacity 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .mhow__step {
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    }
    .mhow__arrow { display: none; }
    .mhow__num {
      font-size: 56px;
      min-width: 60px;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="mhow" id="como-funciona">
  <div class="mhow__inner">
    <div class="mhow__head">
      <h2 class="mhow__head-title magma-animate">Cómo<br>Funciona</h2>
      <span class="mhow__head-sub magma-animate">3 pasos · sin complicaciones</span>
    </div>

    <div class="mhow__step magma-animate">
      <div class="mhow__num">01</div>
      <div class="mhow__content">
        <div class="mhow__step-title">Abrí la Lata</div>
        <p class="mhow__step-body">15 bolsitas listas para usar. Compact, liviana, va a cualquier lado.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mhow__arrow">→</div>
    </div>

    <div class="mhow__step magma-animate">
      <div class="mhow__num">02</div>
      <div class="mhow__content">
        <div class="mhow__step-title">Colocá la Bolsita</div>
        <p class="mhow__step-body">Entre el labio y la encía. Sin agua, sin vapor, sin olor. Discreta y cómoda al instante.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mhow__arrow">→</div>
    </div>

    <div class="mhow__step magma-animate">
      <div class="mhow__num">03</div>
      <div class="mhow__content">
        <div class="mhow__step-title">Sentí el Magma</div>
        <p class="mhow__step-body">100mg de cafeína natural liberados en minutos. Energía limpia y sostenida, sin el crash.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mhow__arrow">→</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

